text: New video has surfaced on Snapchat from a crowded Houston restaurant Wednesday night.  Some people are concerned about a lack of social distancing and face coverings.  Restaurants are currently allowed to be open to 50% capacity. #houston #texas #COVID19 https://t.co/4aVbZVpgKc
